      <title>肯尼亚准备迎接更多 Z 世代抗议税收游行，导致一人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/one-dead-as-kenya-braces-for-more-gen-z-marches-against-taxes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚立法者准备下周就这项备受争议的征税措施进行最终投票，届时将爆发更多游行，警方对抗议拟议增税的抗议活动进行镇压，造成一人死亡，数十人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/one-dead-as-kenya-braces-for-more-gen-z-marches-against-taxes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 09:55:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Veitmane 称投资者因法国风险而买入意大利股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-21/investors-buying-italy-on-french-risk-says-veitmane-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国的痛苦就是意大利的收获？道富银行高级多资产策略师 Marija Veitmane 表示，机构投资者在提前选举之前一直在抛售法国股票，并且在出现大规模抛售之前一直持有。她补充说，有趣的是，法国股票的抛售并没有加速，但意大利股票的买入却很多。她在彭博简报上与 Manus Cranny 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-21/investors-buying-italy-on-french-risk-says-veitmane-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 09:51:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Octopus 将向政府偿还 30 亿英镑以收购 Bulb</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/octopus-will-pay-back-3-billion-to-government-for-bulb-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府在帮助 Octopus Energy Ltd 收购能源危机期间破产的 Bulb Energy Ltd 后，将从 Octopus Energy Ltd 获得 30 亿英镑（38 亿美元）的偿还。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/octopus-will-pay-back-3-billion-to-government-for-bulb-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 09:46:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大亨们准备放弃 Pick n Pay 投票权以吸引投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/tycoons-ready-to-cede-pick-n-pay-voting-power-to-lure-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷蒙德·阿克曼 (Raymond Ackerman) 家族放弃了他们在 Pick n Pay Stores Ltd. 的部分投票权，以帮助这家陷入困境的南非零售商吸引投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/tycoons-ready-to-cede-pick-n-pay-voting-power-to-lure-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 09:45:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区 PMI：经济活动放缓，工厂低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-21/euro-zone-pmi-activity-slows-factory-slump-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区私营部门商业活动的反弹意外失去动力，该地区制造业创下了今年以来最糟糕的一个月。标普全球综合采购经理人指数 6 月跌至 50.8。彭博经济的 Jamie Rush 在彭博电视上讨论了这一问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-21/euro-zone-pmi-activity-slows-factory-slump-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 09:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾金融监管机构誓言放宽规则以促进增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/taiwan-s-finance-regulator-vows-to-ease-rules-to-stoke-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾市场监管机构新任负责人表示，在科技引领的投资热潮中，台湾计划放宽规定，允许金融业在台湾经济产出中占据更大比重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/taiwan-s-finance-regulator-vows-to-ease-rules-to-stoke-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 09:42:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Segantii 返还三分之一基金资产并裁减数十名员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/segantii-returns-a-third-of-fund-assets-and-cuts-dozens-of-staff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，亚洲对冲基金巨头 Segantii Capital Management Ltd. 已将其管理的 47 亿美元资产中的约三分之一返还给投资者。一个月前，这家对冲基金巨头因内幕交易指控而宣布倒闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/segantii-returns-a-third-of-fund-assets-and-cuts-dozens-of-staff</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 09:30:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱沙尼亚阻止欧盟新税收规则出台，该规则可能对 Airbnb 和 Bolt 造成冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/estonia-blocks-new-eu-tax-rules-that-would-have-hit-airbnb-bolt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱沙尼亚正在阻止增值税改革，该改革将对数字平台（包括短期住宿和客运公司，如 Bolt Technology OU 和 Airbnb Inc.）施加新的责任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/estonia-blocks-new-eu-tax-rules-that-would-have-hit-airbnb-bolt</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 09:13:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙的支持率在选举开始前一周创下历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/le-pen-s-party-gains-support-in-poll-macron-approval-drops</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离两轮立法选举开始仅剩一周多的时间，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的支持率周五下跌六个百分点，创下历史新低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-21/le-pen-s-party-gains-support-in-poll-macron-approval-drops</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 06:41:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金老手为银行提供资本减免，并融入 ESG 元素</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/banks-using-srt-capital-relief-are-calling-more-deals-esg</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着银行越来越多地寻求将其信用风险转移给监管较少的投资者，交易的另一端的买家开始要求一项额外的功能：可持续性。]]></description>
